{
  "stem": "1641.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 460.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they came around with this miserable piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He would take two pieces of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That went on here like for two or three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that wasn't enough for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So, eventually, he got one of the knives, and he started to eat his father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He just cut out a piece of wherever there was a bit of flesh to be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He just peeled off a bit of flesh from him, and he was eating him slowly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then, this was all very fine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But after a while, the father started to smell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I mean, dead body.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I mean, it was very cold, so it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Wasn't like in hot weather, it would be worse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was temperature inside was around zero.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Outside it was minus 20.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was eating his father slowly, but we told him that we don't really mind that he eats him, but we objected to the smell.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] finished, whether you like it or not, we are going to report you, and we're going to throw out the body.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] don't report me, just throw him out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's dead now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He just died now, and, OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we threw him out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the dead bodies were pulled outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that stage, there were still a few men who were strong enough to pull out dead bodies from between the beds, hundreds of them every day.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the time came when there was nobody strong enough to pull out the dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then came those last weeks when the dead bodies accumulated between the beds, in the beds, under the beds, between the beds and the toilet.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, actually, the toilets were overflowing, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was jammed up.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
